Package fr.diginamic.entities.associatives

Class WordingEpreuve

java.lang.Object
fr.diginamic.entities.associatives.WordingEpreuve
@Entity public class WordingEpreuve extends Object
Represents a WordingEpreuve in the system. A WordingEpreuve is a name of an Epreuve in a specific language. Table associatives between Epreuve and Langue.
